\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\qc\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
SEP23/BSE/3344U}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\qc\ltrpar\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\sb0\sa180\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\rtlch\afs28 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs28\b\f4\loch
1. Background and Problem Statement}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
\tab University students face increasing mental health challenges caused by academic pressure, financial stress, social isolation, relationship issues and uncertainty about the future. Many students do not seek help early because of stigma, confidentiality concerns, limited awareness of available services and difficulty accessing timely counseling support. As a result, emotional distress may escalate and negatively affect academic performance, social well being and overall quality of life.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
MindCare is proposed as a student-centered mobile solution that provides private, compassionate and accessible mental wellness support in one platform.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\sb0\sa180\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\rtlch\afs28 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs28\b\f4\loch
2. Project Goal and Objectives}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Goal:}{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
 To provide a safe digital space where university students can access counseling, self-help tools and crisis support conveniently from their mobile devices.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\sb0\sa120\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Specific Objectives:}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- To enable secure user onboarding through splash, welcome, login, signup and optional anonymous access.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- To provide an intuitive dashboard for quick access to counseling and wellness services.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- To support appointment booking with counselor, date, time and session type selection.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- To provide mood tracking, self-help resources and private counselor chat features.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- To offer immediate crisis support contacts and breathing exercises for urgent emotional regulation.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li0\lin0\sb0\sa180\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\rtlch\afs28 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs28\b\f4\loch
3.}{\loch
 }{\rtlch\afs28 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs28\b\f4\loch
Target Users}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
\tab The primary users are university students aged approximately 18-30 who need confidential emotional support, preventive wellness guidance, or professional counseling access. Secondary users include students who prefer anonymous exploration before full registration.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\sb0\sa180\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\rtlch\afs28 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs28\b\f4\loch
4. Proposed Solution and Core Features}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
\tab MindCare will be implemented as a  mobile application with a calm, mental-health-focused user interface using teal, soft blue, white and light green tones. The solution includes:}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- }{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
User Authentication:}{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
 login, signup, session handling and anonymous mode.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- }{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Home Dashboard}{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
: greeting, mood check-in, quick access cards and bottom navigation.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- }{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Counseling Booking}{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
: counselor selection, date/time slot selection, appointment confirmation.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- }{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Chat and Support:}{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
 conversation list and counselor messaging flow.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- }{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Mood and Learning:}{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
 mood tracker, trends view, article/resource browsing.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li720\lin720\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
- }{\rtlch\ab \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Crisis Module:}{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
 hotline access, SMS support and breathing exercise guidance.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\fi0\li0\lin0\sb0\sa180\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\rtlch\afs28 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs28\b\f4\loch
5. Implementation Approach}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
\tab The project follows a clean architecture approach with separated layers for presentation, domain models, data repositories and local persistence. Flutter Material Design components are used for responsive, accessible interfaces. SQLite and SharedPreferences are used for local data/session handling in the prototype phase.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\sb0\sa180\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\rtlch\afs28 \ltrch\hich\af4\loch\fs28\b\f4\loch
6. Expected Outcomes and Impact}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
\tab MindCare is expected to improve early help-seeking behavior, increase awareness of available mental health resources and reduce emotional barriers to support among students. The app will also demonstrate practical application of mobile software engineering principles to solve a real social challenge in higher education.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\sb0\sa120\ltrpar\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch

\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af8\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af9\langfe2052\ql\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b\f4\loch
Deliverable: }{\hich\af4\loch\fs24\b0\f4\loch
A functional Android APK prototype with key user journeys, screenshots and project documentation for academic assessment.}
\par }